{
  "stem": "1132.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now at the time-- as I said, I was born in '38-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at that time my father had a thriving law practice.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was doing very well, and the family, as a result, was doing very well financially and economically.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had-- my mother had an uncle in this country who emigrated to the United States in the early 1900s.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he was in touch with the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I have pictures of him and the-- visiting Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And when things started getting bad, the last time he visited Hungary was late '37, early '38, when my mother was pregnant with me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he was begging my parents to leave because he felt that things were getting bad with the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And my parents-- my father said, look, I have a thriving practice here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I've been through World War I.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I survived World War I.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I can't believe that there will be any problems.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So they very kindly turned him down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And of course later on, they were proven to be not so correct in that decision.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Things in Hungary, from what I have been told and from what I do remember, were fine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "My life proceeded on a reasonable basis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "My recollections and pictures I have of myself and my family all show a very happy family from '38 on after I was born.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Now, I have recollections of things starting to happen in '40, '41.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "That's probably stories that I have heard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And that is that they were beginning to give Hung-- Jewish professionals a hard time as far as practicing was concerned.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Things went downhill from that time on.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
